  "CheckTitle": "应删除未使用的网络访问控制列表",
  "CheckType": [],
  "ServiceName": "ec2",
  "SubServiceName": "",
  "ResourceIdTemplate": "arn:partition:service:region:account-id:resource-id",
  "Severity": "low",
  "ResourceType": "AwsEc2NetworkAcl",
  "ResourceGroup": "network",
  "Description": "确保您的虚拟私有云 (VPC) 中没有未使用的网络访问控制列表（网络 ACL）。如果网络 ACL 未与子网关联，则控制失败。该控制不会为未使用的默认网络 ACL 生成发现结果。",
  "Risk": "如果未使用的网络 ACL 在没有目的的情况下保留，它们可能代表潜在的安全风险，因为它们可能稍后被错误地与子网关联。",
  "RelatedUrl": "https://docs.aws.amazon.com/config/latest/developerguide/vpc-network-acl-unused-check.html",
  "Remediation": {
    "Code": {
      "CLI": "aws ec2 delete-network-acl --network-acl-id <nacl_id>",
      "NativeIaC": "",
      "Other": "https://docs.aws.amazon.com/securityhub/latest/userguide/ec2-controls.html#ec2-16",
      "Terraform": ""
    },
    "Recommendation": {
